{"tid":327544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港珠澳大橋　料需分段啟用","createTime":"2017-07-19T00:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T08:01:55.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"83718a04b22bbc57d27df6abf7168943f421d63d","tid":327544,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T00:10:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1860000/1860887/cilf20170405041q_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1860000%2F1860887%2Fcilf20170405041q_1024.jpg&h=d5d598b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港珠澳大橋工程波折重重，當局雖仍以2017年底作為整體通車目標，但連接香港口岸和機場的機場隧道、屯門至赤鱲角連接路南段和北段則分階段完成。有立法會議員批評令大橋效益大打折扣。<br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋工程通車時間會否再延誤惹人關注，當局現時仍以2017年年底完成及具備通車條件作為目標，但整個大橋系統則需要斬件式完成，直至2020年才完全啟用。<br />\n<br />\n路政署提交立法會交通事務委員會文件披露，部分對大橋開通並非必不可少的路段，將會延遲至2018年才完成。<br />\n<br />\n當中包括連接香港口岸和機場的機場隧道，有關道路和交通管制及監察系統工程，以及香港口岸部分綠化及灌溉系統、部分口岸輔助建築物的內部工程，以及部分交通控制及監視系統等。而用以應付長遠運作需求的香港口岸第二階段工程，則會因應口岸開通後的人流及車流，再考慮推展時間表。<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1860000/1860887/0719-LC-MAP_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1860000%2F1860887%2F0719-LC-MAP_1024.jpg&h=2192ffbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n至於銜接口岸與大嶼北的屯門至赤鱲角南面連接路，則會延至最快2019年上半年完成，而貫通口岸至屯門的北面連接路，當局指相關海底隧道工程仍有複雜技術問題，如承建商能充分合作處理，適時提交合理及具成本效益的修改設計，預計最快於2020年完成。<br />\n<br />\n立法會交通事務委員會主席陳恒鑌憂慮，大橋今年底通車，但配套道路未能跟上，新增車流勢加重現時道路負荷，例如來往港珠澳大橋和機場的新增車流，將會繞進東涌，至於來往大橋和屯門的車流，更要在通車後首3年使用青馬大橋，或令青馬大橋塞車。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，物流業是興建大橋的重要作用，分段啟用會令大橋效益大打折扣。但他相信通車首年使用有限，故對現行交通不會構成極大壓力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1860887/%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B%E3%80%80%E6%96%99%E9%9C%80%E5%88%86%E6%AE%B5%E5%95%9F%E7%94%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1860887%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258F%25A0%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A9%258B%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%2596%2599%25E9%259C%2580%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E5%2595%259F%25E7%2594%25A8&d=caRcr3D7oeYocsrgdcR10p7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=a97b5b71\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1860887/%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B%E3%80%80%E6%96%99%E9%9C%80%E5%88%86%E6%AE%B5%E5%95%9F%E7%94%A8</a>"},{"pid":"01b59d3d889930f71a971276c4c466fa1cf02a1c","tid":327544,"uid":1989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T00:25:49.000Z","msg":"用住珠澳段先囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186b66b36890fd7c86f30588a1c8b7c0b26cc0fa","tid":327544,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T00:56:19.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"5b84b282821015c38dce5c6d1a7a532363cfe207","tid":327544,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T02:13:14.000Z","msg":"屯門去機場要轉右上？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd6184a71cf61a28d92dd9f9dc1a26a9b52a342","tid":327544,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T02:25:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屯門去機場要轉右上？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你對香港嘅地理認知有改善空間"},{"pid":"d51293a4911feecd744209bed7036c2bda959dbb","tid":327544,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T02:29:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屯門去機場要轉右上？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你對香港嘅地理認知有改善空間</blockquote><br />\n我諗你冇睇新聞好耐<br />\n港豬大橋要右上"},{"pid":"bce2587c3563d94fb25e0aa5c1323af710ef32fe","tid":327544,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T02:30:04.000Z","msg":"如果係咁<br />\n<br />\n青馬死撚硬 返東涌機場早兩個鐘出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f631f899193193d61cdb906da48e993d2fe3f468","tid":327544,"uid":82641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T02:32:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果係咁<br />\n<br />\n青馬死撚硬 返東涌機場早兩個鐘出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你太高估港豬澳既使用量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f442eef2d38fc47dca2507a539eb648607b870","tid":327544,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T02:35:56.000Z","msg":"人工島飄移<br />\n石屎又唔合格<br />\n其實夠唔夠畀坦克過架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c7fa76ba7e6cb53aa6965aadf69a94315389992","tid":327544,"uid":129111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T03:34:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b671eb6cdda2eaccb91cb81e4aec6085ffad9b","tid":327544,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T04:05:42.000Z","msg":"分階段冧橋"},{"pid":"dae392bc565591d86926acd864303432aff7f46f","tid":327544,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T04:07:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果係咁<br />\n<br />\n青馬死撚硬 返東涌機場早兩個鐘出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你太高估港豬澳既使用量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n除非使用量係0<br />\n否則都係多左"},{"pid":"511eb44e307e0cf6b802a4185220bb04e8a2d8cc","tid":327544,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:54:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屯門去機場要轉右上？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你對香港嘅地理認知有改善空間</blockquote><br />\n我諗你冇睇新聞好耐<br />\n港豬大橋要右上</blockquote><br />\n原來你話行車線<br />\n<br />\n我錯 sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"984f0e61acf68ab800ea3dd4d2cefb199915bae2","tid":327544,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T08:01:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屯門去機場要轉右上？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你對香港嘅地理認知有改善空間</blockquote><br />\n我諗你冇睇新聞好耐<br />\n港豬大橋要右上</blockquote><br />\n原來你話行車線<br />\n<br />\n我錯 sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係出主橋先要咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港境內應該照舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}